description.en:
Kakashi inu v2 is a Collectable NFT and Defi Play to Earn game. Kakashi Inu V2 will have multiple runs of collectable NFTs that are pixelated and non pixelated collectables. The collectables will vary in rank as nonrare, rare and legendary continuously adding to the run. Profits from the NFTs will be distributed as 50% to buyback and burn ,25% to marketing and 25% to game development.
We have 2 games in motion right now game one is a simple spin to win game players earn NFTs and tokens. 
Game 2 is a NFT AR battle game the will be server based so opponents can fight friends and family members. Nfts will be based on anime, marvel characters with copyright laws in consideration. 
NFT collection in production and games are in development.
